title: 11/01/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 11/01/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps Week 8 in the NFL with Albert Breer. Who should the Saints replace Jameis Winston with. The Tampa Bay Times Rick Stroud explains why the Bucs struggle against the Saints. Carson Palmers joins us for the first time since throwing Mike Tomlin's name into the ring for the USC job. And Will Ferrell calls in to discuss his radio Hall of Fame video for DP.
